msgid ""
"We also check whether the player is moving so we can call ``play()`` or "
"``stop()`` on the AnimatedSprite2D."
msgstr ""
"También revisaremos si el jugador (player) se está moviendo llamar a "
"``play()`` (comenzar) o ``stop()`` (detener) en el AnimatedSprite."

